# Force LF line endings for files whose content is hashed or parsed by
# tools that care about exact bytes. Without this, Windows autocrlf rewrites
# checked-out copies to CRLF, which breaks:
#   - sqlx migration checksums ("migration N was previously applied but has
#     been modified" on machines that checked out the same commit on Windows).
#   - tests that compare on-disk file bytes.
*.sql text eol=lf
*.sh  text eol=lf
